name: Make Fun
description: This project has been created in an effort to repay victims of the Sonne Finance exploit that happened in May of 2024. Make.Fun is a launchpad which can permissionlessly create tokens with any amount of liquidity at any arbitrary valuation using a liquidity AMO system. Its native token, called $MF, will be the very first token launched with the new liquidity primitive, with 100% of its supply minted to an Aerodrome LP. There are no team tokens, no investors, and no pre-sale.
